{"word":"G5195 - ὑβρίζω - hybrízō - hoo-brid'-zo - Use despitefully","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑβρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hybrízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoo-brid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Use despitefully"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவமானப்படுத்து, நிந்தி, நிந்தையடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to be insolent; to behave insolently, wantonly, outrageously"},{"paragraph":"2. to act insolently and shamefully toward one"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5196 - ὕβρις - hýbris - hoo'-bris/5196\">G5196</a>; to <i>exercise violence</i>, that is, <i>abuse:</i> - use despitefully, reproach, entreat shamefully (spitefully)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1796 - ἐνυβρίζω - enybrízō - en-oo-brid'-zo/1796\">G1796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5195 - ὑβρίζω - hybrízō - hoo-brid'-zo/5195\">G5195</a>, <a href=\"#/G5196 - ὕβρις - hýbris - hoo'-bris/5196\">G5196</a>, <a href=\"#/G5197 - ὑβριστής - hybristḗs - hoo-bris-tace'/5197\">G5197</a>"}]}